      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">8.1 - 8.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">8.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子墨子言曰：今者王公大人爲政於國家者，皆欲國家之富，人民之衆，刑政之治。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Motse said: Now, all tie rulers desire tieir provinces to be wealthy, their people to be numerous, and their jurisdiction to secure order.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="mozi-008-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-i__align-0002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">mozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">mozi-008-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-i</prop>
