      <prop type="x-confidence">0.93</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">8.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">8.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>然而不得富而得貧，不得衆而得寡，不得治而得亂，則是本失其所欲，得其所惡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>But what they obtain is not wealth but poverty, not multitude but scarcity, not order but chaos — this is to lose what they desire and obtain what they avert.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="mozi-008-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-i__align-0003">
