      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">8.25 - 8.27</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">8.25 - 8.27</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>「始我所恃者，近也，今上舉義不辟遠，然則我不可不爲義。」遠者聞之，亦退而謀曰：「我始以遠爲無恃，今上舉義不辟遠，然則我不可不爲義。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Because the man had the vantage-point. Therefore in administering the government, the ancient sage-kings ranked the morally excellent high and exalted the virtuous. If capable, even a farmer or an artisan would be employed-commissioned with high rank, remunerated with liberal emoluments, trusted with important charges, and empowered to issue final orders.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="mozi-008-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-i__align-0011">
      <prop type="x-work-id">mozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">mozi-008-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-i</prop>
